---
description: Docker image rules
globs:
  - "Dockerfile"
  - ".dockerignore"
alwaysApply: false
---

docker rules:
- Keep image size as minimal as possible.
- Enhance image layering caching capabilities to speed up build time.
- Only use trusted sources for base image and dependencies.
- Only use fixed versions for base images and dependencies.
- Use .dockerignore to ignore files not needed in the image. 
- Avoid running app as root user. 

